---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Substance Use Disorder (SUD) Support - The WEL Foundation">
  <div class="container" style="padding: var(--spacing-8) 0;">
    <header class="reveal-on-scroll" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8); text-align:center; max-width: 800px; margin-inline: auto;">
      <div style="font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">⚕️</div>
      <h1 style="font-size: 3rem; color: var(--color-primary-blue); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">Substance Use Disorder (SUD) Program</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.15rem; color: var(--color-text-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
        Addiction is not a moral failing; it is a complex behavioral health challenge that requires a structured, compassionate, and evidence-based approach. Our SUD programs are tailored to build lasting recovery architectures for our clients.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="grid" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(350px, 1fr)); gap: var(--spacing-6); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);">
      <article class="card reveal-on-scroll stagger-1">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-light-blue);">Intensive Outpatient Program (IOP)</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">
          Designed for individuals requiring rigorous support without the constraints of inpatient hospitalization. Our IOP track provides a concentrated regimen of therapy, typically running 3-5 days a week depending on the clinical assessment.
        </p>
        <ul style="color: var(--color-text-muted); padding-left: var(--spacing-4); line-height: 1.6;">
          <li>Individualized dual-diagnosis clinical assessments</li>
          <li>Frequent toxicological screenings mapped to recovery goals</li>
          <li>Intensive group therapy utilizing Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT)</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="card reveal-on-scroll stagger-2">
        <h2 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-light-blue);">Standard Outpatient (OP)</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">
          Geared toward clients who have achieved a baseline of stability but still require consistent clinical touchpoints to prevent relapse. OP allows clients to maintain their employment and community routines.
        </p>
        <ul style="color: var(--color-text-muted); padding-left: var(--spacing-4); line-height: 1.6;">
          <li>Bi-weekly or weekly 1-on-1 counseling sessions</li>
          <li>Relapse prevention strategizing and trigger mapping</li>
          <li>Seamless integration with Psychiatric Rehabilitation (PRP) services</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

    <section class="reveal-on-scroll" style="padding: var(--spacing-6); background-color: var(--color-bg-offset); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); border: 1px solid var(--color-border); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-8);">
      <h2 style="font-size: 2rem; color: var(--color-primary-blue); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-4);">Our Therapeutic Modalities</h2>
      <div style="column-count: 2; column-gap: var(--spacing-6); color: var(--color-text-main); line-height: 1.7;">
        <p><strong>Cognitive Behavioral Therapy (CBT):</strong> Helping clients unearth the deeply rooted thought patterns and distortions that precipitate substance use, effectively severing the cycle of addiction.</p>
        <p><strong>Dialectical Behavior Therapy (DBT) Skills:</strong> Equipping clients with severe emotional dysregulation the distress-tolerance skills necessary to handle crisis without resorting to chemical coping mechanisms.</p>
        <p><strong>Family Integration:</strong> Addiction reverberates through families. We offer guided family counseling sessions to rebuild trust, set healthy boundaries, and educate loved ones on the neurobiology of recovery.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <div style="text-align: center;" class="reveal-on-scroll">
      <h3 style="font-size: 1.5rem; color: var(--color-primary-blue); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-3);">Ready to take the first step?</h3>
      <a href="/intake/start/" class="btn">Begin Digital Intake</a>
      <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-2); font-size: 0.9rem; color: var(--color-text-muted);">Completely confidential & HIPAA compliant.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
